Clanforge plugin for Slidescreen
================================

This is a plugin for larvalabs' Slidescreen home-screen replacement for android. 
It pulls down information about your servers.

I drew the crappy icon as best I could using:
http://svg-edit.googlecode.com/svn/branches/2.5.1/editor/svg-editor.html 
as it seemed to be the only thing that would generate something Slidescreen 
could render

